<br/>
<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Bloccit</h1>
  <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
  <% if current_user %>
  <p>
    Welcome <%= current_user.name || current_user.email %><br />
    <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
  </p>
  <% else %>
  <p>
      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> or
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!
  </p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Learn Rails</h2>
    <p>Bloccit will help you learn how to write a web application with Ruby on Rails.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Implement Features</h2>
    <p>Learn how to add features to this Reddit Clone and get an idea of how different code
    snippits interact with one another.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Build Your Own</h2>
    <p>Now it's up to you, you should have basic skills to build other applications.</p>
  </div>
</div>
